docs.text: Azure DevOps What is Azure DevOps? Azure DevOps is a series of collaboration and automation tools, formerly known as Visual Studio Team Services. The currently available components are: Azure Boards Azure Pipelines Azure Repos Azure Test Plans Azure Artifacts
